[
    {
        "text": "\"I'm Andy Muschietti,\ndirector of 'It Chapter Two.'",
        "start": 0.71,
        "duration": 3.55
    },
    {
        "text": "So this is the moment where\nall the Losers separate",
        "start": 4.26,
        "duration": 4.03
    },
    {
        "text": "unwillingly.",
        "start": 8.29,
        "duration": 0.95
    },
    {
        "text": "And this is the scene where\nwe find Bill Denbrough--",
        "start": 9.24,
        "duration": 4.68
    },
    {
        "text": "James McAvoy plays\nBill Denbrough--",
        "start": 13.92,
        "duration": 2.79
    },
    {
        "text": "just as after he recovered\nhis bicycle, Silver.",
        "start": 16.71,
        "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
        "text": "This is a great scene, because\nwe summarize a little bit",
        "start": 20.55,
        "duration": 3.52
    },
    {
        "text": "in this escalation\nfrom not being",
        "start": 24.07,
        "duration": 2.21
    },
    {
        "text": "able to ride his bicycle to\nactually getting a grip on it",
        "start": 26.28,
        "duration": 4.44
    },
    {
        "text": "and riding it like a champion.",
        "start": 30.72,
        "duration": 1.95
    },
    {
        "text": "We sort of illustrate how the\nadult turns into the child",
        "start": 32.67,
        "duration": 4.49
    },
    {
        "text": "again.\"",
        "start": 37.16,
        "duration": 1.023
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Hi-ho, Silver!",
        "start": 38.183,
        "duration": 2.151
    },
    {
        "text": "Away!\"",
        "start": 40.334,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "\"And very soon he\narrives to the house",
        "start": 44.32,
        "duration": 2.99
    },
    {
        "text": "where he used to live\nand another memory hits.",
        "start": 47.31,
        "duration": 2.47
    },
    {
        "text": "And it's the memory of that\ninfamous day where he sent",
        "start": 49.78,
        "duration": 4.1
    },
    {
        "text": "Georgie away with a boat.",
        "start": 53.88,
        "duration": 1.89
    },
    {
        "text": "That's a scene that we\ntook from the first movie.",
        "start": 55.77,
        "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
        "text": "So the scene changes\nmood a little bit.",
        "start": 59.37,
        "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
        "text": "The mood is now\na little darker.",
        "start": 62.01,
        "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
        "text": "We know what\nhappened after that.",
        "start": 63.51,
        "duration": 2.49
    },
    {
        "text": "But it's a memory\nthat has been",
        "start": 66.0,
        "duration": 2.07
    },
    {
        "text": "pushed down and pushed down.",
        "start": 68.07,
        "duration": 1.247
    },
    {
        "text": "But the intention\nwith the scene",
        "start": 69.317,
        "duration": 1.333
    },
    {
        "text": "is to like slowly\nlure the audience",
        "start": 70.65,
        "duration": 3.18
    },
    {
        "text": "into this memory\nat the same time",
        "start": 73.83,
        "duration": 3.3
    },
    {
        "text": "that it's happening on\nthe mind of the character.",
        "start": 77.13,
        "duration": 2.5
    },
    {
        "text": "There's a transition\nthat you can",
        "start": 79.63,
        "duration": 1.43
    },
    {
        "text": "see when McAvoy first\narrives to the storm drain",
        "start": 81.06,
        "duration": 3.26
    },
    {
        "text": "and looks at the storm drain.",
        "start": 84.32,
        "duration": 1.79
    },
    {
        "text": "He drops the bike, and\nthe drop of the bike",
        "start": 86.11,
        "duration": 3.62
    },
    {
        "text": "takes us to the past.\"",
        "start": 89.73,
        "duration": 1.26
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Billy, don't leave!\"",
        "start": 101.347,
        "duration": 1.56
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Hello?\"",
        "start": 104.845,
        "duration": 1.59
    },
    {
        "text": "\"The scene continues.",
        "start": 106.435,
        "duration": 1.035
    },
    {
        "text": "We see McAvoy talking\nto a Georgie there.",
        "start": 107.47,
        "duration": 4.72
    },
    {
        "text": "I say 'a Georgie,'\nbecause at this point,",
        "start": 112.19,
        "duration": 2.6
    },
    {
        "text": "we know that Georgie\nisn't Georgie anymore.",
        "start": 114.79,
        "duration": 2.947
    },
    {
        "text": "Georgie has been\ngone for a long time.",
        "start": 117.737,
        "duration": 1.583
    },
    {
        "text": "But because Pennywise is\nplaying with his feelings,",
        "start": 119.32,
        "duration": 3.06
    },
    {
        "text": "he lures him into the illusion\nthat Georgie is still there.",
        "start": 122.38,
        "duration": 5.04
    },
    {
        "text": "Everything that is shot from\nthe outside is location.",
        "start": 127.42,
        "duration": 3.21
    },
    {
        "text": "It's shot on the street.",
        "start": 130.63,
        "duration": 1.35
    },
    {
        "text": "Everything that is\nfrom the inside out,",
        "start": 131.98,
        "duration": 2.96
    },
    {
        "text": "when the camera is\ninside the storm drain,",
        "start": 134.94,
        "duration": 1.75
    },
    {
        "text": "was shot on stage.\"",
        "start": 136.69,
        "duration": 2.85
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Take my hand.\"",
        "start": 139.54,
        "duration": 1.073
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Billy, please.\"",
        "start": 140.613,
        "duration": 0.667
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I've got you.",
        "start": 141.28,
        "duration": 0.361
    },
    {
        "text": "Come on!\"",
        "start": 141.641,
        "duration": 0.539
    },
    {
        "text": "\"He's coming!\"",
        "start": 142.18,
        "duration": 0.583
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Take my hand!\"",
        "start": 142.763,
        "duration": 1.023
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Billy!\"",
        "start": 143.786,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Come on!",
        "start": 144.286,
        "duration": 0.722
    },
    {
        "text": "Take my hand!\"",
        "start": 145.008,
        "duration": 0.962
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I wanted specifically to make\nthis a visual effects shot.",
        "start": 148.92,
        "duration": 3.99
    },
    {
        "text": "As a reference, we had some\nhands of small performers",
        "start": 152.91,
        "duration": 7.05
    },
    {
        "text": "that we used as a reference.",
        "start": 159.96,
        "duration": 1.53
    },
    {
        "text": "The whole swarming is\ndivided in three shots,",
        "start": 161.49,
        "duration": 2.97
    },
    {
        "text": "and it's pretty creepy.\"",
        "start": 164.46,
        "duration": 1.17
    },
    {
        "text": "[LAUGHING]",
        "start": 165.63,
        "duration": 2.55
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I hate you!",
        "start": 168.18,
        "duration": 2.25
    },
    {
        "text": "I hate you.\"",
        "start": 170.43,
        "duration": 2.15
    }
]